H3.text: Which English king was married to Catherine of Braganza from 1662 to 1685. Charles 6

A4.text: Catherine of Braganza was Queen of England, Scotland and Ireland during her marriage to King Charles II, which lasted from 21 May 1662 until his death on 6 February 1685.
